text: Lilliana Belle Ketchman (born June 23, 2008), known as Lilly K., is an American YouTuber, model, and dancer. She is known for being shown on Lifetime's Dance Moms, starting in season six. She is also known for her YouTube videos. ==References== Category:2008 births Category:American dancers Category:American models Category:American YouTubers Category:Living people Category:Models from North Carolina Category:Reality television participants
